<node CREATED="1580507130526" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_79708862" MODIFIED="1580761488146" POSITION="left" TEXT="FreeMind (CRISTIAN)">
<icon BUILTIN="full-1"/>
<node CREATED="1580509665954" ID="ID_1909301928" MODIFIED="1580510082850">
<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
      <b>FreeMind</b>&#160;es un software que permite la elaboraci&#243;n de&#160;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mapa" title="Mapa" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">mapas</font></a>&#160;mentales o de conceptos, programada en&#160;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Google_(lenguaje_de_programaci%C3%B3n)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Google (lenguaje de programaci&#xf3;n) (a&#xfa;n no redactado)" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(165, 88, 88); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(165, 88, 88)">Java</font></a>. Se publica bajo licencia&#160;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/GNU_General_Public_License" title="GNU General Public License" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">GNU o General Public License</font></a>. Esta disponible para<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Microsoft_Windows" title="Microsoft Windows" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">t Windows</font></a>,&#160;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linux" class="mw-redirect" title="Linux" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">Linux</font></a>&#160;y&#160;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mac_OS_X" class="mw-redirect" title="Mac OS X" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">Mac OS X</font></a>&#160;v&#237;a&#160;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Java_Runtime_Environment" title="Java Runtime Environment" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">Java Runtime Environment</font></a>.<sup id="cite_ref-LinuxWorld_3-0" class="reference separada" style="line-height: 1em; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; margin-right: 0"><a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/FreeMind#cite_note-LinuxWorld-3" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null; white-space: nowrap"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">3</font></a></sup>&#8203;<sup id="cite_ref-LinuxLinks_4-0" class="reference separada" style="line-height: 1em; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; margin-right: 0"><a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/FreeMind#cite_note-LinuxLinks-4" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null; white-space: nowrap"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">4</font></a></sup>&#8203;<sup id="cite_ref-InnovationTools_5-0" class="reference separada" style="line-height: 1em; white-space: nowrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; margin-right: 0"><a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/FreeMind#cite_note-InnovationTools-5" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null; white-space: nowrap"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">5</font></a></sup>&#8203;
    </p>
    <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
      FreeMind es &#250;til en el an&#225;lisis y recopilaci&#243;n de informaci&#243;n o ideas generadas en grupos de trabajo, pues con &#233;l es posible generar mapas mentales y publicarlos en internet como p&#225;ginas&#160;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Html" class="mw-redirect" title="Html" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">html</font></a>,&#160;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Java_(lenguaje_de_programaci%C3%B3n)" title="Java (lenguaje de programaci&#xf3;n)" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">java, etc.</font></a>
    </p>
    <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
      FreeMind permite al usuario editar un conjunto de ideas jer&#225;rquizadas alrededor de un concepto central. El enfoque no lineal ayuda al&#160;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brainstorming" class="mw-redirect" title="Brainstorming" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">brainstorming</font></a>, a medida que las ideas se van a&#241;adiendo al mapa mental.&#160;Como aplicaci&#243;n Java que es, FreeMind es portable a trav&#233;s de&#160;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Multiplataforma" title="Multiplataforma" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">m&#250;ltiples plataformas</font></a>&#160;y retiene la misma&#160;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Interfaz_de_usuario" title="Interfaz de usuario" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: null; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: null"><font color="rgb(11, 0, 128)">interfaz de usuario</font></a>, con solo una cierta variaci&#243;n de la interfaz com&#250;n en cada sistema operativo.
    </p>
    <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
      
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
</node>
</node>
